                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>, creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">General's War Banner</span>, summons <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">General's Glory</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">General's War Banner</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br>Your party's characters deal +1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span> (Can stack, Can stack till 3 Rounds)</p>",
